# Where the app loads its dataset + images from.
#
# Web:    leave this UNSET. The web build serves /data and /media from its own
#         origin (same-origin = no CORS), so a relative path is correct.
#
# Native: set this to your deployed site so the Android/iOS app can reach the
#         self-hosted files (native builds have no origin for relative paths).
#         Copy this file to `.env` and fill it in:
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_DATA_HOST=https://mimir.pages.dev
